      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Ready for a rewarding challenge? This vehicle is the ultimate diamond in the rough, perfect for a dedicated hobbyist or restoration expert! While it currently requires comprehensive mechanical work and significant body repairs to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic foundation for someone looking to build their dream car from the ground up. Grab this project at a great price and bring it back to its former glory!",
