    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six. This unit exhibits exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS system. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a rear-mounted M-variable lock differential. The chassis has been proactively addressed with subframe reinforcement plates to ensure torsional rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for superior kinematic control. Finished in Carbon Black, the car shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, but the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. A purist-spec driver\u2019s car with the mechanical pedigree to match.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
